{"type":"article","id":12834,"title":"因為我被喪屍咬了，你也要一齊被咬","uid":11758,"topics":[2186,3821,2836,4978,5089,130],"contents":"<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/LioRo9bl.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LioRo9bl.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/LioRo9bl.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/lHrkffC.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lHrkffC.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/lHrkffC.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n在別的地方轉過來。<br>\n<br>\n不愧是生化危機武漢DLC，全新的地圖，全新的挑戰，但喪屍的行為模式沒有太大變化，仍然是見到未受感染者就撲上去，想全力將對方同化感染，好厲害的大國公民。<br>\n<br>\n現在城市都封了，Leon和Chris平安嗎？<br>\n不過就算逃出來還會追加DLC，快升級成封省了。<br>\n<br>\n你又咬，我又咬，齊齊共享大國的榮耀。","date":"2020-01-24","agreeCount":24,"discussionCount":0}